uientry.unicode: Selection markers show which units are selected.
Path markers show the direction a unit is heading now.
Target zone markers show a unit's area of fire.
Projectile trails make it easier to see projectiles and their current path

state.unicode: Projectile trails make it easier to see projectiles and their current path

uientry.unicode: Projectile trails make it easier to see projectiles and their current path

state.unicode: Help markers show you where ships can disembark and where mountable artillery can be deployed.

uientry.unicode: Determines scale of unit banners. At lowest setting banners will be smaller and will not scale with distance, otherwise they will be larger and scale based on distance from camera.

Determines behaviour of unit tooltips. The default is delayed, which will show the minimal tooltip and then expand to the full tooltip after a short delay. If set to never it will never expand, and if set to always it will always be in the expanded state.
